      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·國風·曹風·001.1</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">蜉蝣.1</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>蜉蝣之羽，衣裳楚楚。心之憂矣，於我歸處。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The wings of the ephemera
Are robes, bright and splendid.
Would they but come and abide with me!</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
