      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·國風·曹風·001.2</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">蜉蝣.2</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>蜉蝣之翼，采采衣服。心之憂矣，於我歸息。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The wings of the ephemera
Are robes, variously adorned.
Would they but come and rest with me!</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
