      <prop type="x-translation-ref">蜉蝣.3</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>蜉蝣掘閱，麻衣如雪。心之憂矣，於我歸說。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The ephemera bursts from its hole,
With a robe of hemp like snow.
My heart is grieved; —
Would they but come and lodge with me!</seg>
      </tuv>
